"title": "5212: arts and crafts",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5212",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Artistic skills, usually practised by craftsmen and passed on from generation to generation, of which a wide variety are mentioned in Scripture.</p>\n<h2>Metalwork</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod39:2-Exod39:3\">EXO 39:2–39:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod31:1-Exod31:5\">EXO 31:1–31:5</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod35:30-Exod35:33\">EXO 35:30–35:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam13:19-1Sam13:21\">1SA 13:19–13:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:13-1Kgs7:14\">1KI 7:13–7:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa41:7\">ISA 41:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer10:9\">JER 10:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts19:23-Acts19:41\">ACT 19:23–19:41</a></p>\n<h2>Stonework</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs5:17-1Kgs5:18\">1KI 5:17–5:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs6:36\">1KI 6:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:9-1Kgs7:12\">1KI 7:9–7:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs22:3-2Kgs22:6\">2KI 22:3–22:6</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr34:8-2Chr34:11\">2CH 34:8–34:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr22:2\">1CH 22:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr2:13-2Chr2:14\">2CH 2:13–2:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek40:42\">EZK 40:42</a></p>\n<h2>Building</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor3:10-1Cor3:15\">1CO 3:10–3:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr34:11\">2CH 34:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra3:10\">EZR 3:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa9:8-Isa9:10\">ISA 9:8–9:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos5:11\">AMO 5:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb3:3-Heb3:4\">HEB 3:3–3:4</a></p>\n<h2>Pottery</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa41:25\">ISA 41:25</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam17:27-2Sam17:29\">2SA 17:27–17:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr4:21-1Chr4:23\">1CH 4:21–4:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa29:16\">ISA 29:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa45:9\">ISA 45:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa64:8\">ISA 64:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer18:1-Jer18:10\">JER 18:1–18:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer19:1\">JER 19:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom9:19-Rom9:21\">ROM 9:19–9:21</a></p>\n<h2>Carpentry</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:13\">ISA 44:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen6:14\">GEN 6:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam5:11\">2SA 5:11</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr14:1\">1CH 14:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs6:31-1Kgs6:33\">1KI 6:31–6:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs12:10-2Kgs12:12\">2KI 12:10–12:12</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr24:11-2Chr24:12\">2CH 24:11–24:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:54-Matt13:55\">MAT 13:54–13:55</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:2-Mark6:3\">MRK 6:2–6:3</a></p>\n<h2>Engraving</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:9-Exod28:12\">EXO 28:9–28:12</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod39:6-Exod39:7\">EXO 39:6–39:7</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:36-Exod28:37\">EXO 28:36–28:37</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod39:30-Exod39:31\">EXO 39:30–39:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:30-1Kgs7:36\">1KI 7:30–7:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr2:13-2Chr2:14\">2CH 2:13–2:14</a></p>\n<h2>Dyeing</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod36:19\">EXO 36:19</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod26:14\">EXO 26:14</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod35:22-Exod35:23\">EXO 35:22–35:23</a></p>\n<h2>Weaving and embroidery</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod35:34-Exod35:35\">EXO 35:34–35:35</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:39-Exod28:40\">EXO 28:39–28:40</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod39:22-Exod39:29\">EXO 39:22–39:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs23:7\">2KI 23:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr4:21\">1CH 4:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa19:9-Isa19:10\">ISA 19:9–19:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa38:12\">ISA 38:12</a></p>\n<h2>Tanning</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:43\">ACT 9:43</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:5-Acts10:6\">ACT 10:5–10:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:32-Acts10:33\">ACT 10:32–10:33</a></p>\n<h2>Making idols</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:1\">LEV 26:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs17:14-2Kgs17:16\">2KI 17:14–17:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:18-Isa40:20\">ISA 40:18–40:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa41:5-Isa41:7\">ISA 41:5–41:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:9-Isa44:20\">ISA 44:9–44:20</a></p>",
